    "title": "Yellow Split Pea Pur\u00e9e with Buttered Onions and Caper Salsa",
    "description": "A Mediterranean-inspired pur\u00e9e of yellow split peas served with buttered onions and caper salsa, perfect as a dip or side dish.",
    "servings": 6,
    "recipeType": "starter",
    "notes": [
      "Make it your own - Veganise it: swap the butter for olive oil.",
      "Serves 6 as a dip, or 4 as a side",
      "Yotam\u2019s love affair with the Mediterranean means those signature staples \u2013 fatty olive oil, salty feta, briny capers! \u2013 permeate both his home kitchen and the OTK. This pur\u00e9e is a take on fava, a Greek mezze dish of yellow split peas with capers and red onion. It\u2019s fantastic served as a dip, but also works alongside grilled fish or roasted meat."
    ],
